::Kluster::

Kluster frowns. "I'm not saying ANY crime, Phobia, but we'll do our best to 
overlook them. However, for security purposes, the computer is programmed to 
recognize all predacons as enemies. If you can deliver your goods outside of 
the range of the defences, my troops could pick them up."

He turns around, shutting off his end of the conversation with Phobia (Phobia 
can talk to him but not hear him).

"Hysteria," he says into his comm, "We'll be having a shipment of technology 
soon. Since you're the techbot, can you check it out?"

He turns back around, once again activating his end of the line to Phobia.
